dct_title_s: Energy Web Atlas natural gas underground storage facilities (USA), 2016
dct_description_sm: Points representing underground natural gas storage fields in the United States as of July 2016. Approximate county centroids are used for map location. Data originate from the U.S. Energy Information Administration.
